00:13:29,820 --> 00:13:31,820
 Especially around impact,

400
00:13:31,820 --> 00:13:33,820
 around purpose.

401
00:13:33,820 --> 00:13:35,820
 What is the point?

402
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:37,820
 We are confronted with a broken world,

403
00:13:37,820 --> 00:13:39,820
 immeasurable needs, and finite

404
00:13:39,820 --> 00:13:41,820
 resources. I can help

405
00:13:41,820 --> 00:13:43,820
 these two people, but

406
00:13:43,820 --> 00:13:45,820
 what about the other hundred that are

407
00:13:45,820 --> 00:13:47,820
 going without any resources?

