00:14:17,820 --> 00:14:19,820
 then there is only one logical conclusion.

424
00:14:19,820 --> 00:14:21,820
 Each and every one of us

425
00:14:21,820 --> 00:14:23,820
 must continue to serve with whatever

426
00:14:23,820 --> 00:14:25,820
 abilities and resources we have.

427
00:14:25,820 --> 00:14:27,820
 The battle we are in may

428
00:14:27,820 --> 00:14:29,820
 be hard, and granted,

