00:14:37,820 --> 00:14:39,820
 share in the victory.

434
00:14:39,820 --> 00:14:41,820
 Let me share

435
00:14:41,820 --> 00:14:43,820
 a very personal thing

436
00:14:43,820 --> 00:14:45,820
 with you for a moment, and maybe this will

437
00:14:45,820 --> 00:14:47,820
 be helpful to some of you.

438
00:14:47,820 --> 00:14:49,820
 I have often felt

439
00:14:49,820 --> 00:14:51,820
 overwhelmed by the brokenness of

440
00:14:51,820 --> 00:14:53,820
 the world, and struggled with periods

