00:18:03,820 --> 00:18:05,820
 That was their main objective, that was

536
00:18:05,820 --> 00:18:07,820
 the "what" of what they were trying to achieve.

537
00:18:07,820 --> 00:18:09,820
 So, let's apply

538
00:18:09,820 --> 00:18:11,820
 then the three practices of being a

539
00:18:11,820 --> 00:18:13,820
 restorative presence. Number one,

540
00:18:13,820 --> 00:18:15,820
 I think we can safely assume

541
00:18:15,820 --> 00:18:17,820
 that the twelve are rooted in Christ. I think we can

542
00:18:17,820 --> 00:18:19,820
 just put that aside. So, number two,

543
00:18:19,820 --> 00:18:21,820
 cultivating

544
00:18:21,820 --> 00:18:23,820
 community. They made a conscious

545
00:18:23,820 --> 00:18:25,820
 choice to cultivate their community

546
00:18:25,820 --> 00:18:27,820
 by including the needs

547
00:18:27,820 --> 00:18:29,820
 of the Hellenistic Jews.

