00:18:37,820 --> 00:18:39,820
 This was part of how

553
00:18:39,820 --> 00:18:41,820
 they approached the "what" of

554
00:18:41,820 --> 00:18:43,820
 their purpose, the ministry of the Word of God.

555
00:18:43,820 --> 00:18:45,820
 They knew that

556
00:18:45,820 --> 00:18:47,820
 going after that goal was not going to be

557
00:18:47,820 --> 00:18:49,820
 possible if they did not change

558
00:18:49,820 --> 00:18:51,820
 how they were doing it on the side.

