 instead embrace how

577
00:19:27,820 --> 00:19:29,820
 you're doing it as a way

578
00:19:29,820 --> 00:19:31,820
 to glorify God.

579
00:19:31,820 --> 00:19:33,820
 Being in the light of God is not only determined

